        value: 4
        type: 5
        typeString: CustomFieldType_Actor
      - title: Menu Text
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Dialogue Text
        value: Leading someone to their afterlife is one thing. But having to do
          so while watching all their friends and family struggeling to let go is
          always hard.
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Sequence
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      conversationID: 1
      isRoot: 0
      isGroup: 0
      nodeColor: 
